Read: To retrieve information about an existing user, weâ€™ll need to look up the User object in our HashMap using the user ID as the key.
Update: To update user information, weâ€™ll need to retrieve the User object from our HashMap using the user ID as the key, and then update the relevant properties of the User object.
Delete: To delete a user from the system, weâ€™ll need to remove the User object from our HashMap using the user ID as the key.

